    <item>
      <title>美元即将抹去今年的全部涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-dollar-edges-closer-to-erasing-all-of-this-year-s-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预期美联储将以比之前预期更快的速度降息以支持经济，美元即将抹去今年的所有涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-dollar-edges-closer-to-erasing-all-of-this-year-s-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国希望德国商业银行“最大程度地独立”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/germany-wants-greatest-possible-independence-for-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府重申反对意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 收购德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG)，称希望德国第二大银行享有“最大程度的独立性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/germany-wants-greatest-possible-independence-for-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:11:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚央行认为林吉特将获得“持久支持”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚央行表示，鉴于马来西亚良好的经济前景和结构性改革，林吉特的强势将持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/malaysia-s-central-bank-sees-enduring-support-for-ringgit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织在 G7 国家中大多数国家上调英国经济增长预期，但警告通胀风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/oecd-upgrades-uk-growth-by-most-in-g-7-but-warns-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们对英国的潜在通胀压力仍存在担忧，但经合组织仍将英国未来两年的经济增速预期上调了，上调幅度超过其他七国集团成员国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/oecd-upgrades-uk-growth-by-most-in-g-7-but-warns-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济走出通胀危机 迈向稳定增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/global-economy-moves-beyond-inflation-crisis-to-stable-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织表示，随着强劲通胀压力缓解，全球经济正在步入新的稳定状态，各国央行得以继续谨慎放松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/global-economy-moves-beyond-inflation-crisis-to-stable-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德意志银行首席财务官否认参与德国商业银行争夺战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-to-stay-on-sidelines-as-unicredit-eyes-commerzbank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行首席财务官詹姆斯冯毛奇周三实际上排除了参与德国商业银行争夺战的可能性，称这家德国最大的银行仍专注于自己的战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-to-stay-on-sidelines-as-unicredit-eyes-commerzbank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村因操纵日本债券市场面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司因涉嫌操纵日本政府债券期货市场而面临 2180 万日元（152,000 美元）的罚款，这对日本最大的经纪公司来说是一个在证券交易复苏期间的挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/nomura-faces-fine-for-bond-market-manipulation-yomiuri-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 05:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
